# Login / auth context

This project was created with `--login`. Auth-related paths:

- Domain: `lib/domain/auth/model/`, `lib/domain/auth/infrastructure/`
- Feature: `lib/features/auth/application/`, `lib/features/auth/presentation/`
- Sign-in form: `lib/features/auth/sign_in_form/application/`, `.../presentation/`
- API interceptor: `lib/apis/interceptors/`
- `ErrorLocalizer.localizeAuthFailure` in `lib/core/errors/error_localizer.dart`

Follow existing auth patterns when extending authentication flows.
